1
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:15,200
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:40,970
[My Dear Guardian]

3
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:44,320
[Episode 11]

4
00:02:40,170 --> 00:02:41,320
Captain.

5
00:02:56,860 --> 00:02:57,560
Captain Liang!

6
00:02:57,650 --> 00:02:59,090
What are you doing here? Leave now!

7
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,410
I'm here to deliver the medicine
and to give you a checkup.

8
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,610
I'm alright. Leave now!

9
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:03,960
How can you be alright?

10
00:03:04,050 --> 00:03:06,080
Xiao Teng said you haven't slept
for days.

11
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:08,210
I'm reminding you as a doctor.

12
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:09,720
You must take a break now!

13
00:03:11,140 --> 00:03:12,040
No need to!

14
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:14,120
Just take a break for a few minutes.

15
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,080
Send her away.

16
00:03:18,250 --> 00:03:20,400
Unless you take a break,
I'm not going anywhere.

17
00:03:20,860 --> 00:03:23,200
Captain, why don't you listen to Dr Xia?

18
00:03:23,290 --> 00:03:24,800
So you're aware that
I'm your captain?

19
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:26,250
Send her away!

20
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:27,800
Listen, Liang Mu Ze.

21
00:03:28,779 --> 00:03:30,090
You should carry out the mission

22
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,410
on the premise that
you take care of yourself.

23
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:34,160
You're made of blood and flesh!

24
00:03:35,330 --> 00:03:36,810
I'm an occupational military officer.

25
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,650
I know my own body's condition.

26
00:03:38,730 --> 00:03:39,610
Send her away!

27
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:40,330
Yes!

28
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:42,670
Don't touch me! Liang Mu Ze!

29
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:46,170
Liang Mu Ze!

30
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:48,010
Keep working! Stay safe!

31
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:48,450
Yes!

32
00:03:48,529 --> 00:03:50,050
Liang Mu Ze, let go of me!

33
00:03:50,140 --> 00:03:51,150
What are you doing?

34
00:03:51,490 --> 00:03:52,800
Liang Mu Ze, let go of me!

35
00:03:52,890 --> 00:03:53,910
Do you hear me?

36
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:55,529
Liang Mu Ze, let go of me!

37
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:56,990
I'm getting angry!

38
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:59,730
Liang Mu Ze, let go of me!

39
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:00,920
I'm getting angry!

40
00:04:02,130 --> 00:04:03,010
Brigade Commander Dong!

41
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,640
Help, Brigade Commander Dong!

42
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:06,640
Liang Mu Ze!

43
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:12,910
Brigade Commander.

44
00:04:13,370 --> 00:04:15,000
What are you doing?

45
00:04:31,820 --> 00:04:32,690
Xiao Teng!

46
00:04:32,770 --> 00:04:34,590
Xiao Teng, what's wrong?

47
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:39,130
Xia Chu.

48
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:40,960
Have some water.

49
00:04:41,130 --> 00:04:42,010
Cool down.

50
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:43,950
Thank you, Brigade Commander Dong.

51
00:04:47,609 --> 00:04:49,670
He's not gentle at all.

52
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:51,640
You need to reflect upon yourself

53
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:53,520
for what has happened today.

54
00:04:53,650 --> 00:04:54,560
As long as she stays away from the dyke,

55
00:04:54,650 --> 00:04:55,830
I'll reflect upon myself on anything.

56
00:04:56,290 --> 00:04:58,150
If I don't go to the dyke,
will you take a break?

57
00:04:58,290 --> 00:04:59,650
Is it the right time for a break?

58
00:04:59,730 --> 00:05:01,470
-As I said, your safety...
-Enough!

59
00:05:04,740 --> 00:05:06,050
How are things going on on your side?

60
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,200
No doubt the water level

61
00:05:07,290 --> 00:05:08,930
at the ten mission areas have reduced

62
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,040
but the water level at three other areas

63
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:11,120
are still above the warning line.

64
00:05:11,610 --> 00:05:13,550
Mission area number two
is the most dangerous one.

65
00:05:16,410 --> 00:05:17,290
What happened?

66
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,630
Don't move. Let me check on him.

67
00:05:24,010 --> 00:05:24,600
He came down with a fever.

68
00:05:24,690 --> 00:05:25,590
Report!

69
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:27,740
Brigade Commander!

70
00:05:28,410 --> 00:05:29,290
Brigade Commander.

71
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:31,240
Something urgent came up
at Dr Wu's camp.

72
00:05:31,810 --> 00:05:32,690
What?

73
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:42,400
Brigade Commander,
the three patients who caught a cold

74
00:05:42,490 --> 00:05:44,359
came down with fevers
higher than 39 degrees Celsius.

75
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,670
They have sore throats,
stuffy noses and body aches.

76
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:48,910
They also suffer from
coughing and diarrhoea.

77
00:05:50,530 --> 00:05:51,480
Report.

78
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:53,450
I need to use the outhouse.

79
00:05:53,530 --> 00:05:54,690
-Tian Yong.
-Yes!

80
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,070
-Bring him to the outhouse.
-Yes.

81
00:06:02,850 --> 00:06:05,630
Brigade Commander, I must not die.

82
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:08,590
I'm the only son in the family.

83
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:11,150
He is still waiting to hand over
the family business to me.

84
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:13,350
Cut the nonsense.

85
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:14,720
Stay in bed.

86
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:16,040
Yes.

87
00:06:16,850 --> 00:06:18,320
Can't you confirm the diagnosis by now?

88
00:06:18,410 --> 00:06:19,600
With the equipment that we have,

89
00:06:19,690 --> 00:06:20,570
I can't confirm the diagnosis.

90
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:22,290
You can report it to the superior
since there are three patients.

91
00:06:22,370 --> 00:06:23,250
It's four.

92
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,840
We have to include the staff officer
who has just passed out.

93
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:29,370
-What's wrong, Xiao Teng?
-I'm having a stomachache.

94
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:30,340
Don't go near him.

95
00:06:30,490 --> 00:06:31,560
Stay back.

96
00:06:31,890 --> 00:06:32,770
Yes.

97
00:06:33,490 --> 00:06:34,290
Brigade Commander Dong.

98
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:35,440
Please arrange manpower

99
00:06:35,530 --> 00:06:37,280
to isolate this tent.

100
00:06:37,530 --> 00:06:38,570
Before the superior unit sends someone

101
00:06:38,650 --> 00:06:40,070
who can confirm the diagnosis,

102
00:06:40,170 --> 00:06:41,210
besides Dr Wu and me,

103
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:42,590
everyone else
has to leave the tent immediately.

104
00:06:44,220 --> 00:06:45,430
Is it really so serious?

105
00:06:45,570 --> 00:06:47,280
Plague always comes after a flood,
Brigade Commander.

106
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,280
Observe the patients closely.

107
00:07:31,370 --> 00:07:32,720
Lower his body temperature.

108
00:07:33,010 --> 00:07:33,890
Yes.

109
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:41,850
Do you feel better?

110
00:07:41,930 --> 00:07:42,990
I'm still not feeling well.

111
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:44,500
You're still not feeling well?

112
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:45,870
-My body is burning.
-Okay.

113
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:51,910
Now, the doctors are doing their best

114
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:53,790
to save our comrades!

115
00:07:54,420 --> 00:07:57,600
We have to hold on to our post

116
00:07:57,890 --> 00:07:59,920
to protect their safety!

117
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:01,330
Got it?

118
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:02,790
Yes!

119
00:08:03,570 --> 00:08:05,470
It's okay, don't worry.

120
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:07,230
Don't be scared.

121
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,830
Finally, it's sunny again.

122
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:34,760
It's finally sunny again.

123
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:39,310
Yes.

124
00:09:48,010 --> 00:09:49,200
Will they recover?

125
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:53,390
Are you scared?

126
00:09:57,170 --> 00:09:58,710
Have you ever met some people in life

127
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:02,040
where you completely trust them

128
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:03,720
and will take a bullet for each other?

129
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:05,800
Have you?

130
00:10:10,330 --> 00:10:11,230
I trust all of them.

131
00:10:14,060 --> 00:10:15,490
Every time I bring them out on a mission,

132
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:16,920
I only have one thought.

133
00:10:17,260 --> 00:10:19,590
I will make sure they're intact

134
00:10:21,690 --> 00:10:23,030
when they go home to their parents,

135
00:10:23,650 --> 00:10:25,070
wives, and children.

136
00:10:31,050 --> 00:10:32,910
The tears of a military officer's
family are too heavy.

137
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:35,600
I can't take it.

138
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:06,260
[Martyr Luo Liang]

139
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:21,990
Meng Zhen.

140
00:11:23,970 --> 00:11:25,070
Don't worry.

141
00:11:26,730 --> 00:11:28,760
We'll always keep you
and your son company.

142
00:11:47,820 --> 00:11:49,320
If I had a choice,

143
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:53,790
I would rather be
the person in the casket.

144
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:56,230
I don't want anything
to happen to my comrades.

145
00:11:57,290 --> 00:11:58,750
That's why when we were in Isaia,

146
00:12:00,020 --> 00:12:01,390
when Lieutenant Tian injured himself,

147
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,760
you overreacted.

148
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:07,790
It's not only because
Tian Yong injured himself.

149
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:11,370
It's also because of
your reckless behaviour

150
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:12,710
when we're organising the rescue.

151
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:13,890
The moment you lifted the robber's gun,

152
00:12:13,980 --> 00:12:15,800
it's no different from committing suicide.

153
00:12:15,890 --> 00:12:16,990
Do you know that?

154
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:19,050
If I didn't give it a second thought

155
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:20,390
and fired the gun at you,

156
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:24,440
I think my career as a military officer
would have stopped then.

157
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,400
I bet the complaint

158
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:28,720
must have caused you so much trouble.

159
00:12:29,450 --> 00:12:31,550
I was number one
in the Hunter Military School assessment.

160
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:33,560
Then, I dropped to number two.

161
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:36,320
Songpaisarn got the advantage for nothing.

162
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,320
I'm sorry.

163
00:12:38,490 --> 00:12:39,370
It's okay.

164
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:40,750
I'll take it back soon or later.

165
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:47,420
How about you?

166
00:12:47,730 --> 00:12:48,640
Are you scared?

167
00:12:49,490 --> 00:12:51,910
Back in 2003, Ms Lan,

168
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,800
who was my mum,

169
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:57,890
was the chief nurse
of the General Surgery Department

170
00:12:57,970 --> 00:12:59,370
of the city's best hospital.

171
00:12:59,460 --> 00:13:01,670
She contracted SARS
when she was taking care of the patients.

172
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:05,160
[Though she survived the disease,]

173
00:13:06,060 --> 00:13:08,000
[her health deteriorated.]

174
00:13:08,930 --> 00:13:10,200
[She had no choice but to retire early.]

175
00:13:10,930 --> 00:13:12,470
[Because of my mum,]

176
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:13,960
[I decided to become a doctor.]

177
00:13:15,130 --> 00:13:16,920
[In the beginning, she was against it.]

178
00:13:17,770 --> 00:13:20,000
[When the admission letter
was sent to my house,]

179
00:13:22,370 --> 00:13:23,670
[she looked at it for a long time.]

180
00:13:26,130 --> 00:13:27,960
[Then, she said,]

181
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:30,870
["Daughter,"]

182
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:33,710
["there's no turning back."]

183
00:13:40,940 --> 00:13:42,040
As a doctor,

184
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:43,680
fear

185
00:13:44,690 --> 00:13:47,230
is one of the human natures
that we have to get over.

186
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:49,030
Instead of feeling scared,

187
00:13:49,820 --> 00:13:51,430
my urge to play my role as a doctor

188
00:13:52,210 --> 00:13:53,830
at disastrous times is stronger.

189
00:13:54,220 --> 00:13:55,510
I don't want to live with regrets.

190
00:13:56,690 --> 00:13:57,570
As such,

191
00:13:58,010 --> 00:13:59,080
no matter what,

192
00:13:59,890 --> 00:14:02,480
I'll guard the dyke.

193
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:04,800
I'll stay committed
and dedicated to my job.

194
00:14:04,970 --> 00:14:06,120
I'll complete my duty.

195
00:14:06,610 --> 00:14:08,030
Before my comrades give up,

196
00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:09,520
I'll never give up.

197
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:12,520
Being committed doesn't mean
you don't have to take care of yourself.

198
00:14:12,850 --> 00:14:14,990
Something bad will happen
if you don't rest well.

199
00:14:15,900 --> 00:14:16,920
Are you worried about me?

200
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:18,050
Yes.

201
00:14:21,370 --> 00:14:22,250
Why?

202
00:14:28,730 --> 00:14:30,440
Why are you worried about me?

203
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:37,280
I'm a doctor, Liang Mu Ze.

204
00:14:38,780 --> 00:14:40,910
I can't stand it when someone
doesn't take care of themselves.

205
00:14:44,450 --> 00:14:45,520
Thank you, Dr Xia.

206
00:14:52,410 --> 00:14:53,590
They're back.

207
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:04,730
Brigade Commander!

208
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:07,330
Brigade Commander!

209
00:15:11,290 --> 00:15:12,170
Sir.

210
00:15:12,380 --> 00:15:14,000
It's the W4C9 virus.

211
00:15:14,530 --> 00:15:15,450
No mutation is detected.

212
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,590
The vaccine is already on the way.

213
00:15:16,930 --> 00:15:18,440
The isolation measures
were executed just in time.

214
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:20,400
We'll wait for the patients
to be vaccinated.

215
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:22,000
Then, conduct blood tests on the soldiers.

216
00:15:22,090 --> 00:15:23,000
We'll give them a talk
on prevention and control

217
00:15:23,090 --> 00:15:24,240
to prevent further infection.

218
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:26,810
Let's start working!

219
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:27,720
Yes!

220
00:15:27,810 --> 00:15:29,350
-Liang Mu Ze!
-Yes!

221
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:30,040
Carry out full protection!

222
00:15:30,130 --> 00:15:31,010
Yes!

223
00:15:32,650 --> 00:15:33,530
Come with me!

224
00:15:40,570 --> 00:15:41,450
See?

225
00:15:41,540 --> 00:15:43,350
As usual, you hold us up again.

226
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:44,740
But,

227
00:15:45,940 --> 00:15:46,920
well done!

228
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:48,350
-Report.
-Come in.

229
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:51,870
Captain, Xiao Teng's fever is gone.

230
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,070
How is he doing?

231
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:54,460
He's doing fine.

232
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:55,630
Xiang Yang is taking care of him.

233
00:16:56,050 --> 00:16:57,470
He's still muddle-headed though.

234
00:16:57,660 --> 00:16:58,590
He kept asking me,

235
00:16:59,170 --> 00:17:00,230
"Where are the angels?"

236
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:01,760
What angels?

237
00:17:01,980 --> 00:17:03,600
When he came down
with the fever, he thought

238
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:05,360
Dr Xia had a pair of wings.

239
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:10,000
Have the medical team left?

240
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:11,670
Not yet, they're on the dyke.

241
00:17:11,980 --> 00:17:13,670
Brigade Commander wants to send them off.

242
00:17:14,330 --> 00:17:15,120
Let's check it out.

243
00:17:15,210 --> 00:17:16,110
Yes.

244
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:23,269
Thank you for your help.

245
00:17:23,420 --> 00:17:24,920
-Don't mention it.
-Otherwise, god knows

246
00:17:25,010 --> 00:17:26,480
what would happen to the soldiers.

247
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:27,809
It's our duty.

248
00:17:27,890 --> 00:17:28,769
Thank you for the hard work.

249
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,350
Salute!

250
00:18:05,970 --> 00:18:07,120
Take care.

251
00:18:08,130 --> 00:18:09,490
I'll wait for you to come home.

252
00:18:12,650 --> 00:18:14,430
All thanks to the doctors,

253
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:18,030
especially Dr Xia.

254
00:18:19,220 --> 00:18:20,520
She looks fragile

255
00:18:20,810 --> 00:18:22,350
but she takes her job so seriously.

256
00:18:22,570 --> 00:18:23,640
Not only is she professional,

257
00:18:24,010 --> 00:18:25,360
she is also kind-hearted.

258
00:18:26,290 --> 00:18:27,560
She is such a nice lady.

259
00:18:29,050 --> 00:18:30,000
What do you think, captain?

260
00:18:33,570 --> 00:18:35,840
What's wrong? Are you having insomnia?

261
00:18:37,140 --> 00:18:40,000
I'm exhausted physically
but my brain keeps me awake.

262
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:41,790
These are my first sleeping pills
since I came here.

263
00:18:43,220 --> 00:18:44,520
Every medicine has its side effects.
Don't...

264
00:18:46,890 --> 00:18:47,770
What's wrong?

265
00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:50,270
Something is wrong with the pills.

266
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:04,350
It looks like an effervescent tablet.

267
00:19:04,460 --> 00:19:05,760
It dissolves in the water right away.

268
00:19:09,740 --> 00:19:11,360
It melts in water.

269
00:19:22,010 --> 00:19:25,040
At ease! Attention!

270
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:26,910
Look to the left!

271
00:19:28,130 --> 00:19:29,880
Eyes front! At Ease.

272
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:31,200
Attention!

273
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:35,870
Later, according
to the order from the superior,

274
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:39,120
besides the injured soldiers
who are recuperating,

275
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:41,470
the rest who are
from combat battalion and Special Forces

276
00:19:41,770 --> 00:19:43,520
are going to Zone Four.

277
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,050
Team Nine of the Special Forces Brigade
will stay back

278
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:48,480
as the reserve team, just in case.

279
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:49,720
Got it?

280
00:19:49,810 --> 00:19:50,830
Yes!

281
00:20:16,570 --> 00:20:18,040
It's the same formula.

282
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:20,630
The smell is so familiar.

283
00:20:24,020 --> 00:20:25,790
Are you done being sentimental?

284
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:29,600
Dr Zhang.

285
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:33,800
How does leading a surgery feel?

286
00:20:35,050 --> 00:20:38,230
Just like a nightmare, it's exciting!

287
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:39,810
Great.

288
00:20:40,130 --> 00:20:42,360
Get ready to enter the theatre.

289
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:43,680
Now?

290
00:20:45,020 --> 00:20:46,890
The heart transplant
which was scheduled earlier

291
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:48,330
had been postponed.

292
00:20:48,420 --> 00:20:50,010
Of course, if you're not keen
to take part in it,

293
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:51,200
you may skip it.

294
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:52,190
I want to join.

295
00:20:52,330 --> 00:20:54,160
-Sure.
-Dr Zhang.

296
00:20:56,020 --> 00:20:56,900
Yes?

297
00:20:57,690 --> 00:20:59,670
Xiao Xiao performed well too.

298
00:21:02,690 --> 00:21:03,320
So?

299
00:21:03,410 --> 00:21:04,050
She would like to watch

300
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,800
the heart transplant surgery.

301
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:06,760
Can both of us

302
00:21:06,850 --> 00:21:07,930
enter the theatre together?

303
00:21:08,020 --> 00:21:09,070
It's full.

304
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:11,960
There's only one vacancy
for a houseman.

305
00:21:14,090 --> 00:21:15,040
Is there any question?

306
00:21:17,330 --> 00:21:18,310
No.

307
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:20,320
All right, hurry up.

308
00:21:28,610 --> 00:21:30,240
-In the next round...
-I won't thank you.

309
00:21:32,410 --> 00:21:34,790
Next time, it'll be me.

310
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:45,890
This place

311
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:47,870
is a battlefield for patients.

312
00:21:48,130 --> 00:21:49,630
It's also a battlefield for doctors.

313
00:21:49,940 --> 00:21:51,930
Everyone who enters this place

314
00:21:52,020 --> 00:21:54,470
is fighting for survival.

315
00:21:55,690 --> 00:21:56,880
For life,

316
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:57,910
dignity,

317
00:21:58,130 --> 00:21:59,170
responsibility,

318
00:21:59,250 --> 00:22:01,600
and the irreplaceable
sense of accomplishment at work,

319
00:22:02,010 --> 00:22:04,560
we put ourselves in tight spots
over and over again.

320
00:22:04,650 --> 00:22:07,030
We fight hard against the God of Death.

321
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:11,930
If I chose the path

322
00:22:12,010 --> 00:22:13,920
because of youth's passion,

323
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:16,190
then being persistent
throughout the journey

324
00:22:16,490 --> 00:22:19,000
is because I have faith in the profession.

325
00:22:19,300 --> 00:22:20,350
As the saying goes,

326
00:22:20,450 --> 00:22:22,050
"The one who wants to wear a crown"

327
00:22:22,130 --> 00:22:23,840
"must bear the weight."

328
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,390
I'm looking for a birthday present
for our daughter.

329
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:30,690
You told me

330
00:22:30,780 --> 00:22:32,910
she likes dolls, right?

331
00:22:37,140 --> 00:22:38,270
She doesn't like it anymore?

332
00:22:41,130 --> 00:22:42,910
All right, I got it.

333
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:46,350
What is it? Say it.

334
00:22:50,530 --> 00:22:52,370
No, no way!

335
00:22:52,460 --> 00:22:53,910
It's not the right time.

336
00:22:55,180 --> 00:22:56,330
When I'm done with my work,

337
00:22:56,420 --> 00:22:57,750
I'll pay her a visit.

338
00:22:59,260 --> 00:23:01,360
I don't know when I can get it done.

339
00:23:03,410 --> 00:23:04,600
Stop speaking in English!

340
00:23:04,690 --> 00:23:05,760
I don't understand English.

341
00:23:07,250 --> 00:23:08,160
Listen...

342
00:23:22,010 --> 00:23:22,890
Li Lei.

343
00:23:23,530 --> 00:23:25,240
Rao Zhi, we found something.

344
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:28,230
Okay, got it. I'm coming back.

345
00:23:30,890 --> 00:23:31,870
How is it?

346
00:23:32,770 --> 00:23:33,650
Rao Zhi.

347
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:35,520
The information is provided by
the Intelligence Bureau.

348
00:23:35,610 --> 00:23:36,490
Xiong

349
00:23:36,580 --> 00:23:37,890
has been scrutinised by the narcotics
squad for a long time.

350
00:23:37,980 --> 00:23:39,450
They suspect that his business

351
00:23:39,540 --> 00:23:40,760
is just a camouflage.

352
00:23:41,130 --> 00:23:43,090
He supplies
a type of Chinese shrub, Ephedra

353
00:23:43,180 --> 00:23:44,410
which is one of the ingredients
to produce crystal meth

354
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:45,760
to drug cartels abroad.

355
00:23:45,850 --> 00:23:47,710
Have the narcotics squad taken any action?

356
00:23:48,460 --> 00:23:49,050
Not yet.

357
00:23:49,140 --> 00:23:50,330
They haven't figured out

358
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:51,720
the mode of communication
and the transaction channel

359
00:23:51,810 --> 00:23:52,970
between Xiong and the purchasers.

360
00:23:53,060 --> 00:23:53,730
Just like us,

361
00:23:53,810 --> 00:23:54,750
they're monitoring him.

362
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,560
Channel?

363
00:24:02,490 --> 00:24:03,470
The City of Desire?

364
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:27,150
[Completing invasion]

365
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:40,660
[Please send the information
to my mailbox.]

366
00:24:51,010 --> 00:24:53,360
Xiao Xiao, let's hang out tonight.

367
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:56,270
I can't make it. I'm on duty.

368
00:24:56,900 --> 00:24:58,030
How about Xiao Chu?

369
00:24:59,220 --> 00:25:01,200
I'll pass. Something happened at home.

370
00:25:02,380 --> 00:25:03,930
I heard that front line flood fighters

371
00:25:04,010 --> 00:25:05,320
have left the disaster area.

372
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:06,730
I guess your beloved military officer

373
00:25:06,820 --> 00:25:08,320
is coming home, right?

374
00:25:09,570 --> 00:25:10,910
He's not mine.

375
00:25:11,250 --> 00:25:12,360
As for his whereabouts,

376
00:25:12,450 --> 00:25:13,590
you have to ask him.

377
00:25:14,130 --> 00:25:15,170
Goodbye, everyone.

378
00:25:15,260 --> 00:25:16,430
Have fun!

379
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:20,440
She's so impatient.

380
00:26:07,290 --> 00:26:09,350
Welcome home, Captain Liang.

381
00:26:10,690 --> 00:26:11,790
I left my key in the military camp.

382
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:13,140
Take it.

383
00:26:14,140 --> 00:26:15,020
What is this?

384
00:26:16,610 --> 00:26:17,630
Give me a hug.

385
00:26:19,450 --> 00:26:21,110
You bought custard steamed buns!

386
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:22,670
Yes, I crave it.

387
00:26:23,130 --> 00:26:24,280
That's why I bought an extra portion.

388
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:38,150
♫ Heart is filled
with your little company everyday ♫

389
00:26:29,490 --> 00:26:32,640
Finally you're back.
I've missed you so much!

390
00:26:39,290 --> 00:26:48,220
♫ Can't miss a thing about you,
hence there is no regrets ♫

391
00:26:49,010 --> 00:26:53,990
♫ Getting used to your habits
from breakfast to dinner ♫

392
00:26:54,230 --> 00:26:57,770
♫ Spending every minute to stay with you ♫

393
00:26:56,330 --> 00:26:57,280
Liang Mu Ze.

394
00:26:58,330 --> 00:26:59,750
You should smile more frequently.

395
00:26:59,850 --> 00:27:02,440
You look quite handsome when you smile.

396
00:27:03,290 --> 00:27:04,270
How shallow.

397
00:27:08,570 --> 00:27:10,230
Come join me for dinner
after you have unpacked.

398
00:27:08,770 --> 00:27:13,390
♫ Liking your habits,
remembering small moments ♫

399
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:16,690
♫ Infecting sorrows with smiles ♫

400
00:27:18,100 --> 00:27:22,900
♫ Getting used to what you like,
trying to be brave ♫

401
00:27:22,980 --> 00:27:29,230
♫ Liking becomes natural
and turns into a habit ♫

402
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:40,980
♫ Even though it's simple, my heart
still fills with deep emotion for you ♫

403
00:27:36,580 --> 00:27:37,800
I do look quite handsome.

404
00:27:39,010 --> 00:27:41,350
How long will it take?
Should I start cooking?

405
00:27:41,650 --> 00:27:43,310
You may cook now! I'm almost done!

406
00:27:42,430 --> 00:27:50,660
♫ We're trying to keep it natural
and romantic at the same time ♫

407
00:27:52,420 --> 00:28:00,730
♫ Every time we slow down,
the whole world is filled with love ♫

408
00:28:02,100 --> 00:28:10,720
♫ Can't miss a thing about you,
hence the path is simple yet dazzling ♫

409
